## Sponsorship Categories

VLDB sponsorships are categorized into two types:

- Conference Sponsorship
- Endowment Sponsorship

The Conference Sponsorship funds a specific conference (such as this year's {{ data.name }}), where the benefits to the sponsors are largely restricted to the time of the conference; while the Endowment Sponsorship provides additional benefits all year round.

